| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3365 — Recovery Inhibition (bianlian)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 90dd5a5e-39a7-54f5-b223-13a03e11a2c6"
